          <actionDate>2018-07-26</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Protecting Taxpayers Act</b></p> <p> This bill modifies the organizational structure, management practices, and enforcement procedures of the Internal Revenue Service (IRS). </p> <p>The bill modifies policies regarding:</p> <ul> <li>the IRS Oversight Board,</li> <li>employee training procedures, </li> <li>tax enforcement procedures, </li> <li>various tax requirements that affect small businesses,</li> <li>the correction of errors by retirement plan administrators, </li> <li> programs that assist low-income taxpayers,</li> <li>the IRS appeals process for taxpayers, and</li> <li>information technology.</li> </ul>]]></text>
        </item>
